OL,3,CIran war: Dubai airports announce
OL,4,C'limited resumption of operations'
OL,6,FAirports in Dubai have announced
OL,7,F"limited resumption of operations" on
OL,8,FMonday, as a small number of flights
OL,9,Fhave been given the green light to
OL,10,Ftake off.
OL,12,FTravellers are being told not to
OL,13,Fproceed to Dubai International Airport
OL,14,For Dubai World Central Airport (Al
OL,15,FMaktoum International Airport) unless
OL,16,Fthey have been contacted directly by
OL,17,Ftheir airline with a confirmed time of
OL,18,Fdeparture.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
