OL,3,CIran war: Dubai airports announce
OL,4,C'limited resumption of operations'
OL,6,FGulf nations have become targets for
OL,7,FIranian strikes as it lashes out
OL,8,Fagainst America's allies in
OL,9,Fretaliation for its joint attack with
OL,10,FIsrael on Iran over the weekend.
OL,12,FThe widespread conflict has led to the
OL,13,Fclosure of airspace in the region,
OL,14,Fleaving hundreds of thousands of
OL,15,FBritons stranded.
OL,17,FThe United Arab Emirates General Civil
OL,18,FAviation Authority said on Monday that
OL,19,Fcertain flights are now operating.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
