OL,3,CIran war: Dubai airports announce
OL,4,C'limited resumption of operations'
OL,6,FDubai-based airline Emirates has said
OL,7,Fit will resume operating "a limited
OL,8,Fnumber of flights" on Monday night and
OL,9,Fsaid it is "accommodating customers
OL,10,Fwith earlier bookings as a priority".
OL,12,FEmirates had previously said it was
OL,13,Fsuspending flights until 3 pm (local
OL,14,Ftime) on Tuesday.
OL,16,FFlyDubai also said it was operating a
OL,17,Flimited number of flights on Monday
OL,18,Fevening, including four flights
OL,19,Fdeparting the city and five more
OL,20,Farriving flights.
OL,26,@qD@LOUrD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
