OL,3,CIran war: Dubai airports announce
OL,4,C'limited resumption of operations'
OL,6,FMeanwhile, a flight heading to
OL,7,FLondon's Heathrow, likely carrying
OL,8,Fstranded UK nationals, has departed
OL,9,Ffrom Abu Dhabi.
OL,11,FThe flight is one of 15 Etihad Airways
OL,12,Fflights to depart from Abu Dhabi in a
OL,13,Fthree-hour window.
OL,15,FDoha-based Qatar Airways said Monday
OL,16,Fits flights remain suspended, with its
OL,17,Fnext update planned for Tuesday
OL,18,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
