OL,3,CIran war: Dubai airports announce
OL,4,C'limited resumption of operations'
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,7,Fsaid that the UK is looking at "all
OL,8,Foptions to support our people"
OL,9,Fcurrently stuck in the Middle East.
OL,11,F"We want to ensure that they can
OL,12,Freturn home as swiftly and safely as
OL,13,Fpossible."
OL,15,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper has
OL,16,Findicated that over 100,000 British
OL,17,Fnationals have registered their
OL,18,Fpresence in the region.
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@^O]uD@JO]
