OL,3,CIran war: Dubai airports announce
OL,4,C'limited resumption of operations'
OL,6,FCooper said a total of around 300,000
OL,7,FBritish citizens are in Gulf countries
OL,8,Ftargeted by Iran.
OL,10,FAirspace closures in the Middle East
OL,11,Fhave resulted in many commercial
OL,12,Fflights being grounded since the
OL,13,Fattacks began on Saturday.
OL,15,FMore than a third of the flights
OL,16,Fscheduled to depart from the UK to the
OL,17,Fregion on Monday were cancelled.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
