OL,3,CIran war: Dubai airports announce
OL,4,C'limited resumption of operations'
OL,6,FBritish Airways said it is "closely
OL,7,Fmonitoring the situation" and has
OL,8,Fcancelled "a number of our flights to
OL,9,Fthe Middle East".
OL,11,FVirgin Atlantic axed two flights to
OL,12,FHeathrow on Monday ` one from each of
OL,13,FDubai, UAE and Riyadh, Saudi Arabia `
OL,14,Fwhile others were rerouted.
