OL,3,CIran war: Dubai airports announce
OL,4,C'limited resumption of operations'
OL,6,FIs it safe to travel to Dubai right
OL,7,Fnow?
OL,9,FThe Foreign Office has warned against
OL,10,Fall but essential travel to the UAE
OL,11,Fdue to ongoing tensions in the Middle
OL,12,FEast.
OL,14,FThose in Bahrain, Israel, Kuwait,
OL,15,FPalestine, Qatar, and the United Arab
OL,16,FEmirates (UAE) have been urged to
OL,17,Fregister their presence with the
OL,18,FForeign Office online.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
