OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1772557910
OL,3,CIran war: Dubai airports announce
OL,4,C'limited resumption of operations'
OL,6,FOut of those nations, the UAE is
OL,7,Fbelieved to have the most Britons
OL,8,Fspread between Dubai and Abu Dhabi.
OL,10,FThe UK Government has used the
OL,11,Fregistration scheme before to provide
OL,12,Furgent updates to people affected by
OL,13,Finternational crises, but it has not
OL,14,Fpreviously needed to deal with so many
OL,15,Fpeople in so many different countries.
OL,17,FBritish nationals are being advised to
OL,18,Ffollow the instructions of local
OL,19,Fauthorities and monitor the Foreign
OL,20,FOffice's travel advice, which
OL,21,Fofficials expect to change rapidly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
